{"openapi":"3.0.0","info":{"title":"FitAI - AI-Powered Workout Planner API","version":"1.0.0","description":"\n# FitAI Backend API\n\nA comprehensive fitness tracking and AI-powered workout generation platform.\n\n## Features\n- ü§ñ **AI Workout Generation** - Gemini 2.0 Flash powered intelligent workout creation\n- üí™ **Exercise Library** - 265+ exercises with detailed instructions\n- üìä **Progress Tracking** - Track sets, reps, weight, and performance metrics\n- üéØ **Goal Management** - Set and track fitness goals with AI recommendations\n- üìÖ **Workout Templates** - Create and save reusable workout plans\n- üìà **Analytics** - Comprehensive workout and progress analytics\n- üîê **Authentication** - JWT-based auth with OAuth (Google, GitHub)\n- üì∏ **Media Upload** - Avatar and progress photos with S3 integration\n\n## Authentication\n\nMost endpoints require authentication using JWT tokens. Include the token in the Authorization header:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your_token>\n```\n\nGet your token by registering or logging in via `/api/v1/auth/register` or `/api/v1/auth/login`.\n            ","contact":{"name":"FitAI API Support","email":"support@fitai.com"},"license":{"name":"MIT","url":"https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT"}},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:5000","description":"Development server"},{"url":"https://api.fitai.com","description":"Production server"}],"components":{"securitySchemes":{"bearerAuth":{"type":"http","scheme":"bearer","bearerFormat":"JWT","description":"JWT authorization header using the Bearer scheme. Example: \"Authorization: Bearer {token}\""}},"schemas":{"Error":{"type":"object","properties":{"success":{"type":"boolean","example":false},"message":{"type":"string","example":"Error message"},"statusCode":{"type":"integer","example":400},"errors":{"type":"array","items":{"type":"object","properties":{"field":{"type":"string"},"message":{"type":"string"}}}}}},"User":{"type":"object","properties":{"_id":{"type":"string"